quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  24,53,"∆Āe woondiri Alla, e hattirde goondooje ma…ď…ďe, si a yamirii …ďe ma …ďe yaltu sanne. Maaku: \"wata on woondu, …óoftaare no anndaa, pellet, Alla ko humpitii…óo ko golloton"
  24,54,"Maaku: \"∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on\". Si …ďe huccitii(runtiima) anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko roonda …óon kon, si on …óoftike mo on feeway, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wanaa yottinngol …ďanngungol"
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ďen gom…óin…ďe e moo…óon …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin O lontinay …ďe ka leydi wano O lontinirnoo non …ďen adii…ďe …ďe, ma O wee…ďinan …ďe diina ma…ď…ďe ka O welanaa …ďe, ma O wattitan …ďe …ďaawo kulol ma…ď…ďe ngol hoolaare, Yo …ďe rewam wata …ďe sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yeddu…óo …ďaawo …óum haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe woni faasiqii…ďe …ďen"
  24,56,"√Ďii…ďee e Julde totton Jakka on …óofto…óon kadi Nulaa…óo on, bela jo'o on Yurmete"
  24,57,"Wata a sikku …ďeen yeddu…ďe …ďe laawoto ka leydi, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde"
  24,58,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe, yo sakkintino e moo…óon …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, e …ďen …ďe yottaaki koy…óol immorde e moo…óon, laabi tati ko adii Julde Peeral nden, e tuma wallinton conci moo…óon ka njolloro e ka …ďaawo Julde gee∆īe ko awraaji moo…óon tati non. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fawaaki …ďe …ďaawo majji, jinndoo…ďe hakkunde moo…óon, yoga e moo…óon e dow yoga. Ko wano nii Alla …ďanngini- rani on Aayeeje …óen Alla ko O Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  24,59,"Si sukaa…ďe moo…óon yottike kellefuyee, yo …ďe sakkitinono wano duŇčinornoo non …ďen adii…ďe …ďe, ko wano nii Alla …ďannginiranta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, Alla ko O Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  24,60,"E sonnaa…ďe jottii…ďe …ďen, …ďen …ďe jortaaki desal bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe nde …ďe wallinta conci ma…ď…ďe …óin hara …ďe wonaa fe√Ī√Īin…ďe cu…óaari, ko nde …ďe nantotoo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďe, Alla ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  24,61,"Bakkaatu fawaaki bun…óu on, bakkaatu fawaaki la∆īu…óo on, bakkaatu fawaaki nawnu…óo on, fawaaki e wonkiiji moo…óon nde √Īaamoton ka cuu…ói moo…óon maa…óum ka cuu…ói baabiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói neeniraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói musi…ó…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói banndiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói bappiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói yaayiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óom ka cuu…ói kaawiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói neeniraa…ďe moo…óon ka dewol, maa…óum …óin …ói jogi…óon cottir…óe muu…óum, maa…óum gi…óo moo…óon. Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde hawtoton √Īaamon maa…óum √Īaamon ko on sertu…ďe. Si on naatay e cuu…ói salminee e dow wonkiiji moo…óon, hiwraango immorde ka Alla barkinaango laa…ďungo, ko wano nii Alla …ďannguniranta on Aayeeje …óen belajo'o onon on haqqilay"
  24,62,"Anndu gom…óin…ďe …ďen ko …ďen gom…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ďe laatike hi…ďe wonndi e makko e dow fiyaake moftu…óo, …ďe yahatah haa …ďe duŇčinoo e makko, pellet, …ďen …óa…ď…ďiray…ďe ma duŇčayee ko …ďen …óon woni gom…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ďe …óa…ď…ďirii ma duŇčayee fii yoga e fiyaake ma…ď…ďe, duŇčano on mo yi…óu…óaa [duŇčanaade] e ma…ď…ďe, insinano…óaa …ďe ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,63,"Wata on wa…óu noddugol Nulaa…óo on hakkunde moo…óon wano noddugol yoga e moo…óon yoga. Gom…óii Alla no Anndi …ďen sortotoo…ďe e moo…óon e moltagol, …ďen wonu…ďe lunndaade yamaruyee makko on, yo …ďe rento fii wata fitina hi…ďu …ďe maa…óum Lempte muusu…óe he…ďa …ďe"
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla heeranii ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi gom…óii hiMo Anndi ko wonu…óon e hoore mu'un kon, √Ďalnde …ďe ruttetee faade ka Makko O yeetoo …ďe ko …ďe gollunoo kon. Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde"